D3Edit

A visual code editor for the multivalued database D3 made ​​in Java to make developers life easier.

Features:

    Syntax higthlight
    Code completion (keywords, templates and functions)
    Theme, font and color customize
    Undo/Redo
    Find/Replace
    Compile 

Requirements:

    D3 version 6 or later
    Java Runtime Environment

How to Use:

    1. Install and startup jd3 on the server (http://sourceforge.net/projects/jd3/)
    2. Compile and catalog the routine 'RLISTA' on the server
    3. Run D3Edit, go Edit > Settings and configure


